WEBVTT

00:11:30.003 --> 00:11:32.321
and renews it every five years.

00:11:33.189 --> 00:11:36.720
What Singapore teaches us
is not just the importance of continuity,

00:11:36.744 --> 00:11:39.991
but also the critical role
of autonomy and discretion.

00:11:40.747 --> 00:11:43.772
Cities need the power
to be able to issue debt,

00:11:43.796 --> 00:11:45.010
to raise taxes,

00:11:45.034 --> 00:11:46.185
to zone effectively,

00:11:46.209 --> 00:11:47.865
to build affordable housing.

00:11:49.095 --> 00:11:53.498
What cities need is nothing less
than a devolution revolution,

00:11:53.522 --> 00:11:56.738
and this is going to require
renegotiating the terms of the contract

00:11:56.762 --> 00:11:58.121
with a nation-state.

00:11:58.765 --> 00:12:00.039
Second: